# Design Decisions & Constraints

## AssetCard — Draft Nodes (Picks That Conveyed)

- **Layout:** Top band (year | round) → picture (80px) → bottom band (Pick | #). Bands are **glued above/below** the picture.
- **Never overlay** year, round, Pick, or # on the player picture.
- **All player nodes same size:** 148×168. Bledsoe, Missi, drafted picks — uniform.
- **HEADSHOT_SIZE = 80** for all player nodes.

## User Preferences

- Change only what is asked. If asked to change picture size only, do not move bands or overlay text.
- Do not increase node size.
- Reduce wasted space; avoid excessive spacing.

## Current Constants

- CARD_WIDTH: 148
- CARD_H: 168
- HEADSHOT_SIZE: 80
